Power on 120 sec. config WiFi

SSID: doorbell
PASS: do0R6311

To use set WiFi and FritzBox credentials.

Input (on GPIO16) is 3.3V to 24V AC/DC.
Jumper connects to reset pin (if needed).

Debug: USB serial connection 115200 8N1.

Very loosely based on:
https://www.heise.de/select/ct/2017/17/1502995489716437
https://www.reichelt.de/magazin/projekte/smarte-tuerklingel/
https://github.com/belzetrigger/esp-FritzKlingel

Hardware:
Wemos D1 Mini ESP32
PC814 with 820 Ohm
GPIO16 with internal pullup and PC814 to GND
Jumper from GPIO16 to RESET (not used)
